Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.17,0:00:02.06,中文,,0,0,0,,【血族】前情回顾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Previously on The Strain...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:03.45,中文,,0,0,0,,就像是死尸一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Looks like a dead animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.45,0:00:06.33,中文,,0,0,0,,里面静静地坐着两百多个乘客\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There have been 200 people sitting there silently,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:08.58,中文,,0,0,0,,-一点动静都没有 -我的天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- absolutely no movement. - Oh, my God...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:10.32,中文,,0,0,0,,-你看到了吗 -他们全都死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Are you seeing this? - They're all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:12.87,中文,,0,0,0,,-没有挣扎的痕迹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- No signs of struggle. -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:15.17,中文,,0,0,0,,-发现幸存者了 -我以前见过这种疾病\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- We've got survivors! - I've seen this disease before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:17.53,中文,,0,0,0,,如果棺材还在你手里 他就没办法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If you have the coffin, then you still have him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:21.28,中文,,0,0,0,,你必须在黎明前开过桥回到曼哈顿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You will cross the bridge back into Manhattan before daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:22.90,中文,,0,0,0,,他们会放你过去的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You will be let through.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:24.71,中文,,0,0,0,,封锁机场周边出口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Seal off the perimeter of the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.54,中文,,0,0,0,,收到 我说了放行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Got it. I said let him through.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:34.21,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:37.93,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:39.51,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.98,中文,,0,0,0,,我好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:53.78,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(840,514)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}布鲁{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}克林{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)} 红钩{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}区{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 理{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}查兹{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}街
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:47.68,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 嗯哼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hi. Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:53.00,中文,,0,0,0,,干得好 小杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.10,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸也要大开杀戒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:15.36,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(840,514)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}曼{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}哈{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}顿{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)} 下东{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)}区{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)} D{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}大道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.44,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿哟 西装佬\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey yo, Waxy Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:05.70,中文,,0,0,0,,西装佬 我把你要的箱子带来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Waxy Boy, I got your box!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.80,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:26.13,中文,,0,0,0,,这里面到底有什么 你们这些白人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What you got there, white boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:09.35,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(910,514)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}肯{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}尼{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}迪{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}机场{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 货物{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}D{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.54,中文,,0,0,0,,证件上写着他的名字是彼得毕晓普\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}His lanyard says his name is Peter Bishop,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:14.78,中文,,0,0,0,,航空交通管制的主管 你认识他吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}an ATC supervisor. You knew him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:16.51,中文,,0,0,0,,他的头哪去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where is his head?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:19.05,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是他的头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That is his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我以为你们早就习惯这种场面了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I thought you guys were used to shit like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:23.77,中文,,0,0,0,,他不是医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's not a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.96,中文,,0,0,0,,要把他的头骨压碎到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It would take a lot of pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.26,中文,,0,0,0,,这种程度得要很大压力才行 是什么造成的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to crush his skull like that. What did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.37,中文,,0,0,0,,塔台说他是和你一起下来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The tower said he came down here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.33,中文,,0,0,0,,他在帮我们找一个里吉斯航空753\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He was helping us look for a large cabinet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.30,中文,,0,0,0,,航班上的大柜子 那个柜子不见了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}from Regis 753 that went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:38.50,中文,,0,0,0,,里面有什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What was in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我们认为是一些类似致病原的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We think it was some sort of infectious agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.61,中文,,0,0,0,,你是说就是那东西杀死了飞机上的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You mean whatever killed the people on that plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.26,中文,,0,0,0,,我们还不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:49.65,中文,,0,0,0,,现在一切只是理论 是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, it's just a theory at this point. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:53.22,中文,,0,0,0,,氨的味道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ammonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:56.69,中文,,0,0,0,,-跟飞机上的一样 -你们有谁带着紫外线灯的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Just like on the plane. - Hey, one of you got an ALS?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.76,中文,,0,0,0,,把工作灯关掉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kill the work lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:08.37,中文,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What is that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.90,中文,,0,0,0,,某种生物的排泄物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Biological discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:13.67,中文,,0,0,0,,跟鸟粪差不多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Closest analogue is guano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:16.71,中文,,0,0,0,,或者是虱子的 那只虱子得有多大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That or tick shit. That's one hell of a tick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我是古德温泽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Goodweather.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.21,中文,,0,0,0,,金 你怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim, what's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:27.15,中文,,0,0,0,,整整一夜 没睡过 估计是咖啡喝太多了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Long night. No sleep. Maybe too much coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:31.02,中文,,0,0,0,,该死 我不在乎他们说什么 给我拦住他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Goddamn it! I don't care what he said! Just stall them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:33.02,中文,,0,0,0,,脱光他们的衣服 什么都行 把他们拖住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Lose their clothes. I don't care, just keep them there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.16,中文,,0,0,0,,直到我过去 我们得走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}till we get there. We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:37.39,中文,,0,0,0,,疾控中心接管了这个现场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This crime scene is now under CDC authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.46,中文,,0,0,0,,任何人都不能碰那个尸体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nobody touches that body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.50,中文,,0,0,0,,巴尔内斯刚把那四个幸存者放了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barnes just released the four survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:48.11,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(716,508)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}肯尼迪{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}机场{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)} 疾控{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}中心{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)}临时{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}隔离{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:52.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你不用打的 我的司机会送你过去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't need a cab. My driver will drop you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.20,中文,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 各位 你们不能离开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sorry, folks, but you're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:56.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你就别白费力气了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Spare yourself the crucifixion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:58.68,中文,,0,0,0,,你别想留住我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't have a chance in hell of making that stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:00.05,中文,,0,0,0,,你现在还以为这是什么超级流感吗 医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You still think it's some super flu, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你没看新闻吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Haven't you seen the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:05.12,中文,,0,0,0,,有人把里吉斯航空的报告泄露到网上了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Someone leaked the Regis Air documents to the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:08.06,中文,,0,0,0,,只是一氧化碳中毒 但是被航空公司总裁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's carbon monoxide poisoning. All of it covered up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.06,中文,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔 弗拉克斯敦 隐瞒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}by the airline's CEO, Daniel Flaxton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:12.10,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以安心了 医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You should be relieved, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.26,中文,,0,0,0,,已经不关你的事了 现在你不介意的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's out of your hands. Now if you don't mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:17.77,中文,,0,0,0,,-我还得去提出诉讼了 -你相信电视里说的一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I've got a lawsuit to file. - You believe everything on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.57,中文,,0,0,0,,天哪 这人好烦 我们没事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Holy Jesus, is this man annoying. We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:23.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都很好 就不谢谢你了 医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're all fine. No thanks to you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:26.08,中文,,0,0,0,,现在感觉没事不表示你们没病\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Feeling fine at this moment does not mean you're not sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.48,中文,,0,0,0,,-有些病是有潜伏期的 -我知道了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Diseases incubate. - Look, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.85,中文,,0,0,0,,这是你受尽万众瞩目\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is your time in the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.78,中文,,0,0,0,,升职加薪的好机会 我们很乐意帮你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To snag a promotion. Love to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.05,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我在日蚀那天有个演唱会 所以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but I've got a major concert on the day of the eclipse, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我得走了 真的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need to go. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.82,中文,,0,0,0,,如果由我来决定的话 我想留下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If it were up to me, I'd stay,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.79,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我的律师要我出去 所以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but my union lawyers want me out, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.83,中文,,0,0,0,,别绕圈子了 我现在把话说清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're going around in circles here. Let me be very clear:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:46.83,中文,,0,0,0,,你们都在我的命令下被隔离在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you're all staying here under quarantine on my authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.20,中文,,0,0,0,,巴尔内斯局长说过我们可以走的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Director Barnes said we would be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我说你们得留下 不管他怎么说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I say you stay. I don't care what Barnes said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.37,中文,,0,0,0,,根据健康权利法案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}According to the Health Powers Act,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.41,中文,,0,0,0,,只要有两个医师同意 隔离指令就可以生效\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it only takes two physicians to issue a quarantine order.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:01.45,中文,,0,0,0,,想要来真的吗 我打个电话就可以让你丢掉工作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's on. One phone call, I get your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:04.15,中文,,0,0,0,,-还有马菲特小姐也一样 -现在赶紧打\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- And Little Miss Muffet's. - You better start dialing then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:07.95,中文,,0,0,0,,在打了 凯特 我是琼 帮我接通卫生与公众服务部\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dialing. Katie, it's Joan. Get me the Secretary of Health
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:10.05,中文,,0,0,0,,部长 格丽特皮尔森 的电话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and Human Services, Margaret Pierson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:12.06,中文,,0,0,0,,在昨晚的新闻发布会上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}At a press conference last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.86,中文,,0,0,0,,纽约的疾控中心首席医疗官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Ephraim Goodweather, chief medical officer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:17.36,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗雷姆古德温泽博士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}with the Centers for Disease Control in New York City,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:20.25,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(944,510)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h石心{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}集团{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}\N曼哈顿{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)} 第55{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)}街西{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)} 156{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.43,中文,,0,0,0,,说现在给他的调查\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}said it was too early
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.47,中文,,0,0,0,,-下结论还过早 -这可是个麻烦啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- in his investigation... - This could be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.94,中文,,0,0,0,,疾控中心封锁了机场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The CDC has closed the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.44,中文,,0,0,0,,他们还没释放生还者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They have still not released the survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.24,中文,,0,0,0,,如果他们继续把这个当成传染病\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If they continue to treat this as an epidemic,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:35.48,中文,,0,0,0,,-我们的时间可能会被拖延 -一个小时后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- it will delay our timetable. - In an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:37.95,中文,,0,0,0,,没有人会再说传染病这回事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}nobody will be talking about an epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:40.82,中文,,0,0,0,,四个生还者也能出来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I'll have the four survivors on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.72,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么做到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You will accomplish this how?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.56,中文,,0,0,0,,提供虚假情报\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Disinformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.69,中文,,0,0,0,,一个好故事往往比事实更容易被接受\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A good story always trumps the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.89,中文,,0,0,0,,只需要给媒体一个攻击对象就行了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just give the press a villain to hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:56.63,中文,,0,0,0,,现在 既然这事解决了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now that this is done,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我什么时候能见他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}when do I see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.57,中文,,0,0,0,,很快了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:04.14,中文,,0,0,0,,他已经过河了 这是我们约定好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's across the river. That was our deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:07.01,中文,,0,0,0,,你很快就能见到他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You will see him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你要去哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.95,中文,,0,0,0,,去见个老朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To see an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:16.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我已经读完了里吉斯航空\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I personally read all 250 pages
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:18.21,中文,,0,0,0,,250页的报告\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of the Regis documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:21.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我对航空公司\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I was shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.55,中文,,0,0,0,,不顾乘客安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}by the airline's flagrant disregard
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.78,中文,,0,0,0,,的行为感到震惊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for the safety of its passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.69,中文,,0,0,0,,亚拉伯罕 赛特拉基安\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Abraham Setrakian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.22,中文,,0,0,0,,你的律师来见你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your lawyer's here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:33.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我没有律师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have no lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:14.57,中文,,0,0,0,,你老了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You've grown old,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:18.00,中文,,0,0,0,,A230385\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A230385.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.44,中文,,0,0,0,,艾霍斯特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eichorst...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:24.96,中文,,0,0,0,,-见到我惊讶吗 -都这么多年了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Surprised to see me? - It has been many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.21,中文,,0,0,0,,你看起来还是那个样子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You look exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:32.24,中文,,0,0,0,,你的心跳乱了 我能听出来 犹太人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your heartbeat is irregular. I can hear it, Jew,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.71,中文,,0,0,0,,像钟声一样清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}clear as a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:37.08,中文,,0,0,0,,棺材过河了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did the coffin cross the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.22,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:44.06,中文,,0,0,0,,你的主人现在在哪呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And where is your Master now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:47.53,中文,,0,0,0,,他在通过我看着你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Watching you through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:50.70,中文,,0,0,0,,犹太人 游戏结束了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The great game is over, Jew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.83,中文,,0,0,0,,只要我还有一口气在 就不会让游戏结束\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not while I still breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:57.30,中文,,0,0,0,,真厉害\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:01.54,中文,,0,0,0,,尽管所有证据都显示你会失败\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Despite all evidence to the contrary,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:04.11,中文,,0,0,0,,你还是坚信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you cling to the delusion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:06.11,中文,,0,0,0,,你会成功\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that you will prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:08.51,中文,,0,0,0,,别跟我说你还相信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't tell me you still believe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你们的神\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in that God of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.55,中文,,0,0,0,,他现在在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So where is He?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:14.72,中文,,0,0,0,,为何他毫无动静\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why has He done nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.79,中文,,0,0,0,,面对现实吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Face the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:22.29,中文,,0,0,0,,他只是你们虚构出来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He is nothing but a figment of your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.93,中文,,0,0,0,,你的逮捕报告里说你被捕的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your arrest report says you were apprehended
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:30.34,中文,,0,0,0,,身上带有一把古剑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}with an antique sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:33.04,中文,,0,0,0,,-是萨都的剑吗 -不用担心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Is it Sardu's? - Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:38.81,中文,,0,0,0,,我会在适当的时候还给你的主人的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I will give it back to your Master in due time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:41.58,中文,,0,0,0,,真有趣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That is amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.78,中文,,0,0,0,,还有她的心脏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And her heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.05,中文,,0,0,0,,你现在还保留着吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you still have that as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:53.43,中文,,0,0,0,,你还真多愁善感呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, you are such a sentimentalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.36,中文,,0,0,0,,你可能很想知道这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You might like to know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:11:00.23,中文,,0,0,0,,她到死都在反抗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She struggled at the very end,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.47,中文,,0,0,0,,但是她没哭出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but she never cried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:06.24,中文,,0,0,0,,很奇怪 连啜泣都没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I thought that strange. Not even a whimper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.94,中文,,0,0,0,,只是一直喊着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Only a single word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:10.77,中文,,0,0,0,,亚拉伯罕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Abraham."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.35,中文,,0,0,0,,但是你不在那\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But you were not there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.52,中文,,0,0,0,,帮不了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:19.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你后悔吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you feel great regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我会替她报仇的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I will avenge her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:24.59,中文,,0,0,0,,你什么仇都报不了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You will not avenge anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:26.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你不是英雄 也不是救世主\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're not a hero or a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你只是一个编号\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're just a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:32.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我拿走了你的名字 给了你一个编号\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I took your name and gave you that number.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.10,中文,,0,0,0,,这是你所有的东西了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's all you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.04,中文,,0,0,0,,对你来说呆在这里是一件好事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's good for you that you are in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:46.85,中文,,0,0,0,,这是唯一能让你有安全感的地方了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's the only place you can feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:50.78,中文,,0,0,0,,比在大街上还安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Safer than the streets will be very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:53.55,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You might survive
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:56.39,中文,,0,0,0,,活久一点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:58.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我要你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I want you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:01.93,中文,,0,0,0,,眼睁睁看着事情发生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to watch it unfold, unable to do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.70,中文,,0,0,0,,却无能为力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.90,中文,,0,0,0,,你死之前\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And when you die,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.24,中文,,0,0,0,,最后看到的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it will be the Master's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:15.47,中文,,0,0,0,,将会是我主人的眼睛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you see last...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:18.94,中文,,0,0,0,,还记得你的老朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Remember your old friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.45,中文,,0,0,0,,德雷福希文吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dreverhaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你想知道为什么他不能在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Would you like to know why
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:29.22,中文,,0,0,0,,和你一起共享此刻的荣耀吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}he isn't here to share your glory with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:35.06,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我用那把剑把他碎尸万段了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because I cut him to pieces with that sword
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.26,中文,,0,0,0,,然后将尸体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and dumped his parts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.70,中文,,0,0,0,,扔进了北海\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in the North Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:43.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我相信 你们很快就可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll see that you're reunited with him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.28,中文,,0,0,0,,团聚了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.93,中文,,0,0,0,,走着瞧吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Until next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:59.92,中文,,0,0,0,,A230385\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A230385.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.98,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(808,508)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}曼{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}哈顿{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)} 哈莱姆{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}区{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 东{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}115{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}街
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.29,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈 我回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mama, I home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:31.30,中文,,0,0,0,,她正准备做弥撒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's getting ready for Mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:37.41,中文,,0,0,0,,为什你不收拾一下你的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why don't you clean your shit up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:39.64,中文,,0,0,0,,不要说话 看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shh! Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:42.85,中文,,0,0,0,,-飞机满载着尸体回来了 -我说什么来着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Plane coming in wit those stiffs on it? - What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.92,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.58,中文,,0,0,0,,-你以为我是在和你说着玩吗 -回来了 儿子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You think I'm playing with you? - Hola, mijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.19,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hola, mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:53.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你好吗  你看起来漂亮极了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Como estas? Mira, que linda! You look beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:55.89,中文,,0,0,0,,你看起来 糟透了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You look... terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:58.93,中文,,0,0,0,,儿子 我不喜欢你像这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, mijo. I don't like you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:01.83,中文,,0,0,0,,工作到这么晚 这对你不好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}working nights like this. It's not good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:03.77,中文,,0,0,0,,-我知道 -和我一起去弥撒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I know. - Come to Mass with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:05.74,中文,,0,0,0,,科特斯神父一直问起你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Father Cortez has been asking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我去不了 妈妈 我要去睡觉了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't, Mama, I gotta get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:11.01,中文,,0,0,0,,下星期吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:14.55,中文,,0,0,0,,你看到克里斯宾给我的东西了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did you see what Crispin got me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:16.61,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我没看见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, I didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.68,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.92,中文,,0,0,0,,这东西可真不错 你从哪弄来的 兄弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's a nice piece. Where'd you get it, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.06,中文,,0,0,0,,跳蚤市场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Flea market.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.46,中文,,0,0,0,,便宜得跟白捡的那样 那个老女人不知道她这东西是啥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Was a real steal. Old lady didn't know what she had.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:31.83,中文,,0,0,0,,很高兴我的两个孩子又聚到一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So good to have my two kids together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:35.77,中文,,0,0,0,,你们今晚都会在这吃饭吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your both will here for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.67,中文,,0,0,0,,-是的 妈妈 -我要做点特别的菜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Si, Mama. - I'll make something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.64,中文,,0,0,0,,-好的 -拜拜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- OK. - Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:43.31,中文,,0,0,0,,-拜拜 妈妈 我爱你 -我也爱你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Bye, Mommy, I love you. - I love you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:53.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你从哪得到这个的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where'd you get it? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:56.69,中文,,0,0,0,,你从哪得到这个的 说实话 你个废物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where d'you get it? The truth, you junkie piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.82,中文,,0,0,0,,说啊 说啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.91,中文,,0,0,0,,离这几个街区的那间当铺 那个买银器的犹太人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The pawn shop a couple blocks down! The Jew who buys silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你别把偷回来的垃圾带进这房子里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't bring stolen shit into this house
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.61,中文,,0,0,0,,-还把妈妈拉下水 -好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- and involve Mom on it. - OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.03,中文,,0,0,0,,-你听到了吗 -听到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You hear me? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.98,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 格斯 你竟然还有胆量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know, Gus, you got some balls
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:17.34,中文,,0,0,0,,和我这样说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}talking to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.28,中文,,0,0,0,,两年了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.28,中文,,0,0,0,,你在北部的这两年来 我听着她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Two years I listened to her cry herself to sleep at night
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.95,中文,,0,0,0,,每晚哭着入睡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}while you were upstate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:25.22,中文,,0,0,0,,我才是唯一一个陪着她的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was the only one who was here for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:27.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你拿着她的血汗钱买药嗑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You were shooting her paychecks up your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:29.96,中文,,0,0,0,,-好吧 被你说中了 -是啊 我说中了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- OK, you got me. - Yeah, I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.63,中文,,0,0,0,,好啊 那你呢 格斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}OK. But what about you, Gus, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:34.36,中文,,0,0,0,,-我什么 -距离下次你再被逮住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What about me? - How you long is it gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:38.33,中文,,0,0,0,,再伤透她的心还要多久 哼？\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}before you get busted again and break her heart? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我要把这钟还回去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm taking this clock back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:47.17,中文,,0,0,0,,那也洗不掉你的罪恶 大圣人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's not gonna wash you clean , altar boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你反驳了我的明确指令\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You contradicted my explicit orders
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.80,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(766,520)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}肯尼迪{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}机场{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)} 疾控{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}中心{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)}临时{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}指挥{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:50.06,中文,,0,0,0,,还宣称要对他们进行隔离检疫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and declared them quarantined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:51.17,中文,,0,0,0,,你不能放了这些幸存者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You can't release those survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.53,中文,,0,0,0,,除非我们弄清楚我们面对着的是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not till we know what we're facing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:55.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我们很清楚 让我给你介绍\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We do know. Let me introduce you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.75,中文,,0,0,0,,卫生与公众服务部的部长\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to the Secretarof Health and Human Services,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:58.12,中文,,0,0,0,,玛格丽特·皮尔森\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Margaret Pierson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:00.02,中文,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 古德温泽博士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pleasure to meet you, Dr. Goodweather.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:03.32,中文,,0,0,0,,马丁内兹博士 让我向你们讲一下最新情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Martinez. Let me bring you both up to speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:05.59,中文,,0,0,0,,这些里吉斯航空的报告\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}These Regis Air documents
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:09.20,中文,,0,0,0,,指出了航班753上出现了一个系统故障\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}point to a systems failure aboard flight 753.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:12.53,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我已经让联邦航空局禁飞了里吉斯航空的全部航线\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So I've had the FAA ground the entire Regis Airline fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.87,中文,,0,0,0,,直到国家运输安全委员会完成调查\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}until the NTSB completes its investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.64,中文,,0,0,0,,这不仅仅是疾控中心的案子了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's not a CDC case anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:20.27,中文,,0,0,0,,国家运输安全委员会已经接受这个案子了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The NTSB has the ball now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.01,中文,,0,0,0,,恕我直言 部长\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}With all due respect, Madam Secretary,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:24.04,中文,,0,0,0,,这些人不是死于一个航空系统故障\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}these people didn't die from a faulty air system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.18,中文,,0,0,0,,-不是吗 -我调查出来的所有线索\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- They didn't? - Everything in my investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.18,中文,,0,0,0,,都指向一种致命的病原体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}points to a virulent pathogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:30.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我们远远没有弄清到底发生什么事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're far from understanding exactly what did happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:33.02,中文,,0,0,0,,但我们需要关闭这个机场以防止它传播\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but we need to shut down this airport so it doesn't spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.02,中文,,0,0,0,,-伊弗 冷静 -古德温泽博士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Eph, please. - Dr. Goodweather,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我很欣赏你的热情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I appreciate ur zeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.86,中文,,0,0,0,,但你需要往后退一步 好好考虑一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But you need to step back for a moment and consider
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.86,中文,,0,0,0,,医疗检疫的影响\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the impact of a medical quarantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:43.50,中文,,0,0,0,,那会致使纽约通向世界各地的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It would immediately stop all exports
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.83,中文,,0,0,0,,所有出口贸易立即停止\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}from New York to he rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.07,中文,,0,0,0,,单凭一个预感 你就想要断送70亿的经济贸易\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you want to crash a $70 billion economy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:51.07,中文,,0,0,0,,让股票市场来一次自由落体吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and send the stock markets into a free fall on a hunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.77,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗 我知道你在你的个人生活中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eph, I know you've been under a lot of stress
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.54,中文,,0,0,0,,一直都承受着很大压力 这是很主要的原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in your personal life, that's a big part of the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:56.98,中文,,0,0,0,,-但不要把你的负担 -我的个人生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- But don't bring your baggage... - My personal life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:58.88,中文,,0,0,0,,和这个没有一点关系 这关乎救人性命\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}has nothing to do with this. It's about saving people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:02.55,中文,,0,0,0,,就是那么简单 伊弗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's that simple. Eph...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:04.22,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 艾弗雷特 我不应该那么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry, Everett. I shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:06.52,中文,,0,0,0,,对 你不应该\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, you shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.19,中文,,0,0,0,,接下来这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here's what's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:10.19,中文,,0,0,0,,你要放几天假\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're going to take a few days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:12.43,中文,,0,0,0,,然后等这件事一平息 我们再来讨论\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Then once this all blows over, we're going to revisit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:17.67,中文,,0,0,0,,你的情况 而现在  这件事与你无关了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}your situation. As now, you're no longer involve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:19.77,中文,,0,0,0,,回家吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.05,中文,,0,0,0,,您好 这里是纽约\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You've reached the office
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:30.71,中文,,0,0,0,,首席法医的办公室\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of the Chief Medical Examiner of New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.52,中文,,0,0,0,,暂时无人接\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No one is available to take...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我找不到班尼特 或者是任何人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't reach Bennett, or anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.02,中文,,0,0,0,,他们就不能接下法医办公室的电话吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why aren't they picking up at the coroner's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:39.96,中文,,0,0,0,,他们手上有206个尸体 他们估计有点忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They got 206 dead bodies, they're probably a little busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:51.46,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(806,506)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}皇后{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}区{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}霍华德{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}海滩{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} {\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}科尔曼{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}广场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:59.34,中文,,0,0,0,,雷德芬机长 感谢你愿意见我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Captain Redfern? Thanks for agreeing to meet us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:01.65,中文,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:05.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我的乘客和机务人员都相信我能把他们安全带到肯尼迪国际机场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My passengers and crew trusted me to get them to JFK safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:08.79,中文,,0,0,0,,但我没做到 我想知道为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I didn't. I'd like to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.42,中文,,0,0,0,,你看起来有点苍白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You look a little pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.53,中文,,0,0,0,,我没事 只是有点头痛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm OK. A bit of a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.33,中文,,0,0,0,,耳朵有点耳鸣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's that humming in my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的确有一个非医学上的问题想问你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We do have a non-medical question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:22.37,中文,,0,0,0,,有一大件货物从飞机上失踪了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A large piece of cargo has gone missing from the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:25.58,中文,,0,0,0,,那个箱子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the box
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.11,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道那箱子的事吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know about the box?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:32.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我当时在机上做起飞前的巡查\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was doing my pre-flight walk around on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.59,中文,,0,0,0,,四个穿着制服的官员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Four officials in suits show up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:37.29,中文,,0,0,0,,坐着政府用车 带着这大箱子出现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in a government van with this huge crate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:40.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我们之前也运送过紧急的高级机密货物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've carried last-minute high- security cargo in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.33,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我也没多想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so I didn't think much of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.80,中文,,0,0,0,,这个箱子 是不是9×4英尺\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This box, it was maybe nine foot by four foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.55,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:49.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道是什么政府部门吗 他们是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you know what government office? Who they were?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.64,中文,,0,0,0,,他们下车后从停机坪走上我的飞机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They got down onto the tarmac to my plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:54.64,中文,,0,0,0,,他们穿着制服 带着徽章\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}they had suits and badges...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:56.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道这一定是公务员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I figured it had to be official.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.44,中文,,0,0,0,,但我有什么资格去质问呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Who am I to question this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.48,中文,,0,0,0,,但就是因为我没有去问\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But because I didn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.85,中文,,0,0,0,,206个人死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}206 people are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:07.12,中文,,0,0,0,,其他人依然有危险 但你能救他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Other people are still in danger. You can help save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:10.05,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以去圣塞巴斯蒂安的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here's what you can do: go to the emergency room
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.09,中文,,0,0,0,,急救室\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}at St. Sebastian's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:14.53,中文,,0,0,0,,有位威廉姆·莱斯特医生会在那接见你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A Dr. William Lester will meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:16.99,中文,,0,0,0,,他是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:19.10,中文,,0,0,0,,他是我所认识的最好的诊断专家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's the best diagnostician I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.53,中文,,0,0,0,,他会将你当作私人病患进行收治\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He'll admit you as a private patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:23.67,中文,,0,0,0,,算是帮我个忙 做一些检测\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}as a favor to me, and run some tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:26.37,中文,,0,0,0,,他会找到是什么原因导致你的耳鸣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He'll find out what's causing the sound in your ears
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:27.97,中文,,0,0,0,,-和头痛 -好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- and your headaches. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:35.35,中文,,0,0,0,,真是难以置信 这么费劲地折腾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Unbelievable. Jumping through all these hoops
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:38.42,中文,,0,0,0,,就是因为那些混蛋不愿意进行检疫隔离\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because those bastards don't want to face a quarantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:42.49,中文,,0,0,0,,航空公司怕承担责任\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And the airline's worried about their liability,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我的工会也是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}my union is worried about theirs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.82,中文,,0,0,0,,每个人的头等大事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everyone's first priority
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:49.13,中文,,0,0,0,,都是保障自身\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is covering their asses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.20,中文,,0,0,0,,没有一个人在乎真相\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And no one gives a shit about the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:53.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我在乎 你也在乎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I do, and you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.83,中文,,0,0,0,,而这是现在我们最大的筹码\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and that's the best shot we've got right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.20,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 我的天哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, my God...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:03.41,中文,,0,0,0,,它的口腔有锯齿状的突起物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Its buccal cavity has serrated projections.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.68,中文,,0,0,0,,所以它能抓住或者刺穿任何组织\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So it can latch onto or cut through tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我想试点东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I want to try something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.15,中文,,0,0,0,,得快点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.85,中文,,0,0,0,,在我们被盘问之前搞定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Before someone asks what the hell we're doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:19.62,中文,,0,0,0,,如果这些寄生虫真的感染了受害者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If these worms did infect the victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:22.11,中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(630,54)}向性反应是一种生物学现象 指生物受环境因素刺激而向某特定方向移动或生长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:22.13,中文,,0,0,0,,那么人类血液就会产生一种向性反应\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}then human blood should produce a tropic reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.84,中文,,0,0,0,,快看那个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:49.95,中文,,0,0,0,,是扎克 我应该过去谈谈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's Zack. I'm supposed to stop by to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:51.85,中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(572,164)}爸爸 你还好吗：（ 担心你  ——扎克\N今晚事儿太多了 去睡吧 宝贝 明天打给你 爱你 ——爸爸\N今天你会过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:52.62,中文,,0,0,0,,-监护权听证会的事了 -你最好过去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- the custody hearing. - You better go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:54.83,中文,,0,0,0,,不了 这更重要 他会理解的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, this is important. He'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:57.29,中文,,0,0,0,,他会理解成他并没有你的工作重要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He'll understand he's not as important as your work,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:59.80,中文,,0,0,0,,这也正是他每天所听到他妈妈说的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}which is exactly what he hears from his mother every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:03.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你想要法官把完全监护权判给凯莉吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You want the judge to give Kelly full custody?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:03.64,中文,,0,0,0,,当然不想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.33,中文,,0,0,0,,那就去啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Take a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:10.67,中文,,0,0,0,,雷德芬的检测结果没几个小时是出不来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Redfern's test results won't come in for a couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:13.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我会搞定这个的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:14.73,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:33.28,中文,,0,0,0,,医院见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}See you at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:43.23,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(892,506)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}曼{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}哈{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}顿{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}14街{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 西{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}547{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:46.37,中文,,0,0,0,,-你在这里做什么 -瓦西里·费特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What are you doing in here? - Vasiliy Fet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:49.80,中文,,0,0,0,,-城市害虫控制中心的检察员 -周日也来吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Inspector, City Pest Control. - On a Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:52.20,中文,,0,0,0,,不 你现在不能进行检查\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No! You're not doing an inspection now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:54.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我们没时间 这是我们的香槟早午餐时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's no time... this is our champagne brunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:56.47,中文,,0,0,0,,一周内最忙的服务时段\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Busiest service of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.47,0:21:59.84,中文,,0,0,0,,-抱歉 我们收到投诉 -你想要吃早餐吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Sorry. We had a complaint. - You want breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:02.11,中文,,0,0,0,,跟厨师点餐就好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Give the order to one of the line chefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:05.11,中文,,0,0,0,,但我不会给你任何现金\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I am not giving you any cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你以为我到这来就为了这个吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that what you think I'm here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:10.15,中文,,0,0,0,,哈 看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ha! Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:12.42,中文,,0,0,0,,看到那个了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:14.82,中文,,0,0,0,,那是鼠尿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's rat urine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:17.36,中文,,0,0,0,,真是荒谬 好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ridiculous! OK,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:20.63,中文,,0,0,0,,两百美元 你立刻给我滚出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}two hundred dollars, but you get the hell out of here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.63,0:22:23.93,中文,,0,0,0,,-不 -这会是个错误的决定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- No. - You're making a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:26.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我做过很多错误的决定 但从没断错过害虫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I make many mistakes, but not about vermin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.44,0:22:32.04,中文,,0,0,0,,走开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:36.88,中文,,0,0,0,,那可是个价值3百万的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That was a $300,000 offer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:39.01,中文,,0,0,0,,30分钟的视频采访邀请\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for a 30-minute on-camera interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.51,0:22:42.00,中文,,0,0,0,,-而你就这样挂了电话 -不管他们开出什么条件\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- And you hang up?! - Whatever they're offering,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:43.06,中文,,0,0,0,,跟我们从航空公司拿到的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it's gonna be chump change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:44.38,中文,,0,0,0,,比起来 都不算什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}compared to what we'll get from the airline.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:47.72,中文,,0,0,0,,这可能会被归类于 一夜爆红\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This may go in the category of "Too soon,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:49.29,中文,,0,0,0,,但销量却一路飙升\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but ticket sales are way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:51.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我就爱你这点 鲁比\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's what I love about you, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:53.75,中文,,0,0,0,,敬大难不死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here's to being alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:57.91,中文,,0,0,0,,作为一个艺术家 在这样的时刻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Moments like this... As an artist,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.91,0:23:00.04,中文,,0,0,0,,这样的事情让你后退一步\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}they make you take a step back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:02.20,中文,,0,0,0,,-静观大局 -去质问 为何是我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- and look at the big picture. - There's no answer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:05.57,中文,,0,0,0,,是没有答案的只不过是运气好点  但我欣然接受\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to "Why us." It's just random luck, but I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:16.64,中文,,0,0,0,,-又来了 哼鸣声\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- - There's that... hum again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.13,0:23:19.31,中文,,0,0,0,,你也能听到 对吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You hear it still, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.84,0:23:21.00,中文,,0,0,0,,就像是回声一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's almost like an echo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:23.76,中文,,0,0,0,,像是某种声音的回响\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Like an echo of a voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.76,0:23:26.36,中文,,0,0,0,,可能是当你耳朵或者鼻子堵住的时候 听到的你自己的声音\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}maybe your own voice, when your ears and nose are stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.36,0:23:28.70,中文,,0,0,0,,-真奇怪 -我没听到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- It's weird. - I'm not hearing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:31.60,中文,,0,0,0,,不过加布 如果那声音有曲调 记得写下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but Gabe, if that voice has a tune, write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:34.47,中文,,0,0,0,,这让我想起我的第一次迷幻之旅\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Reminds me of my first acid trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:38.51,中文,,0,0,0,,你嗑过迷幻药吗 琼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You ever done acid, Joan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:40.48,中文,,0,0,0,,没 没嗑过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nope, no acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:42.44,中文,,0,0,0,,迷幻药不是我的菜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.45,0:23:44.48,中文,,0,0,0,,什么才是你的菜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What is your thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:46.68,中文,,0,0,0,,想要去别的地方嗨皮吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You want to take this party someplace else?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:48.15,中文,,0,0,0,,比如说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Like?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:50.22,中文,,0,0,0,,我新影院上面的联排别墅\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Townhouse above my new theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:52.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以庆祝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We can celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:54.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我们逃过一劫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}our escape from the abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.99,0:24:09.92,中文,,0,0,0,,不了 我还是回家吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, I better get home
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.92,0:24:12.49,中文,,0,0,0,,去见见我的孩子们 还有我的丈夫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and see my kids. And my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:14.66,中文,,0,0,0,,不如下次吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe another time?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.53,0:24:17.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我明天要去公司和我们的法律团队汇合\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm going to be getting together our legal team
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:20.06,中文,,0,0,0,,我们很快会再见面的 加布\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}at the firm tomorrow. We'll talk soon, Gabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.43,0:24:26.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我得放松一下 鲁比\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need to get my pipes cleaned, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:29.24,中文,,0,0,0,,挑几个身材火辣的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pick out a couple of hot ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.71,0:24:38.95,中文,,0,0,0,,所有人都停下手中的工作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everyone stop what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.95,0:24:41.25,中文,,0,0,0,,不要再把食物端出厨房了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No more food goes out of the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.25,0:24:43.65,中文,,0,0,0,,现在 赶紧开始打扫清理\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}As of right now, you start cleaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.65,0:24:45.99,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你们还想重新开业的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}if you ever want this place to open up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.99,0:24:47.62,中文,,0,0,0,,你不能让我们关门\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You can't shut us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.63,0:24:50.56,中文,,0,0,0,,香卡议员每周三都会来这里用餐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Councilwoman Shankar eats here every Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.56,0:24:53.40,中文,,0,0,0,,是吗 那你打算给他吃这个喽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh yeah? You gonna serve her this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.00,0:24:57.27,中文,,0,0,0,,各位 请注意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Attention, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.27,0:24:59.64,中文,,0,0,0,,卫生部门已经下令\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}By order of the health department, this establishment
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.64,0:25:02.27,中文,,0,0,0,,将这餐厅关闭 清楚了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is now closed. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.27,0:25:07.59,中文,,0,0,0,,所有人都出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everyone must leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.80,0:25:16.30,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 亲爱的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.30,0:25:20.60,中文,,0,0,0,,赶紧走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.91,0:25:23.17,中文,,0,0,0,,看来我们不用付钱了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm guessing we don't have to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.96,0:25:30.25,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(858,518)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}曼{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}哈顿{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)} 第{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}57街{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)}西{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)} 156{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}号
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.17,0:25:30.11,中文,,0,0,0,,莫西医生带来了好消息 先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Moise called with some good news, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.12,0:25:32.95,中文,,0,0,0,,新肝脏又强壮又健康 是一个工人的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The liver's young and healthy. It belongs to a laborer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.95,0:25:34.72,中文,,0,0,0,,他没有亲人 不会被人发现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No family. He won't be missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.72,0:25:36.15,中文,,0,0,0,,莫西想尽快把它给移植\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Moise would like to move ahead with the acquisition.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.15,0:25:38.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我还不确定我是否需要用它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not sure I'll need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.73,0:25:40.59,中文,,0,0,0,,请恕我直言 先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}With all due respect, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.60,0:25:42.99,中文,,0,0,0,,如果这些人不能履行他们的承诺的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}if these other people can't deliver what they've promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.99,0:25:45.73,中文,,0,0,0,,他们会履行的 马上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They can. And they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.08,0:25:49.33,中文,,0,0,0,,即便如此 您也应该以防万一\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Even so, you should have a backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.26,0:25:51.93,中文,,0,0,0,,您要知道 飞到波哥大要五个小时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep in mind: it's a five-hour flight to Bogota.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.04,0:25:54.00,中文,,0,0,0,,去取肝脏至少得要八个小时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Minimum of eight hours to harvest the organ.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.01,0:25:55.77,中文,,0,0,0,,现在又要多花五个小时飞回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Five more to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.77,0:25:58.31,中文,,0,0,0,,您的肝脏功能已经异常衰竭了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your liver functionality is already well below normal.
