Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.35,0:26:05.32,中文,,0,0,0,,除非已经换了新的肝脏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}until we receive the replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.32,0:26:08.25,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 我知道了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.25,0:26:10.99,中文,,0,0,0,,- 那就做吧 - 我觉得离开这栋楼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Do it. - I'm not sure it's wise
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.99,0:26:15.26,中文,,0,0,0,,不太明智 先生 感染会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to leave the building, sir. Infection will--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.26,0:26:17.69,中文,,0,0,0,,对我承担手术的能力不利\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Adversely affect my ability to withstand surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.69,0:26:20.63,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我知道 我要走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes, yes, yes. I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.63,0:26:23.20,中文,,0,0,0,,不用再多说什么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There is no debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.20,0:26:26.17,中文,,0,0,0,,事实上 我一生中从来没有像这次一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In fact, I've never felt more excited about a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.17,0:26:29.60,中文,,0,0,0,,对接下来的会面如此激动过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.65,0:26:38.15,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(860,516)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}皇后{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}区{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)} 伍德{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}赛德{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 凯{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}尔顿{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}街
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.06,0:26:41.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我也这么觉得 诺拉 101华氏度没有什么好紧张的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I agree, Nora: 101 degrees is not cause for alarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.70,0:26:45.01,中文,,0,0,0,,不过我也不希望他的体温继续上升\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but I don't like that his temperature's rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.39,0:26:48.32,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 等雷德芬的报告出来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Fine. I'll meet you back at the hospital by the time
