Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.00,0:26:56.43,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.11,0:27:00.13,中文,,0,0,0,,等会联系 抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Talk soon. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.13,0:27:03.13,中文,,0,0,0,,- 是关于飞机事件 - 嗯 我也一直关注着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- It's the airplane case. - Yeah, I've been watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.14,0:27:05.24,中文,,0,0,0,,但为什么你会牵扯进去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But why are you involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.24,0:27:07.17,中文,,0,0,0,,他们说那架飞机有问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They say something was wrong with the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.17,0:27:09.14,中文,,0,0,0,,完全是胡说八道 没有人想要得到真相\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's total bullshit. Nobody wants to deal with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.14,0:27:10.91,中文,,0,0,0,,真相是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.66,0:27:13.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.77,0:27:15.28,中文,,0,0,0,,还没进展\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nothing's adding up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.93,0:27:17.31,中文,,0,0,0,,- 这也太可怕了 - 没错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- That's scary. - It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.13,0:27:20.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我很庆幸是你在处理\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, I'm glad you're handling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.44,0:27:24.59,中文,,0,0,0,,这意味着无论是什么问题都会被解决\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That means whatever needs to be done will get done.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.13,0:27:27.09,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.84,0:27:29.86,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 进来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.88,0:27:32.62,中文,,0,0,0,,马特在里面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Matt's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.33,0:27:38.60,中文,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 伊弗 - 嗨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Hey, Eph. - Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.26,0:27:42.11,中文,,0,0,0,,戴安 我叫戴安 我和你见过差不多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Diane. My name's Diane. I've met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.11,0:27:44.72,中文,,0,0,0,,有五次了 我每隔一天会开车送你孩子上学\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}five times. I drive your kid to school every other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.00,0:27:46.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你都还记不住我的名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and you can't even remember my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.48,0:27:48.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我记得你的名字 戴安 刚刚只是没有想起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I remember your name, Diane. I just drew a blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.64,0:27:49.78,中文,,0,0,0,,真有趣 对你我颗可从来没有想不起来过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Funny, I've never drawn a blank about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.78,0:27:51.72,中文,,0,0,0,,一次也没有 为什么呢 伊弗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not once. Why is that, Eph?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.20,0:27:54.49,中文,,0,0,0,,戴安 扎克在后面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Diane. Zack's in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.49,0:27:57.36,中文,,0,0,0,,- 帮马特的忙 - 在干什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- helping Matt. - Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.82,0:27:59.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我们正在把你的老办公室\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're converting your old office
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.29,0:28:00.37,中文,,0,0,0,,改造成游戏室\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}into a game room.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.28,0:28:10.66,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.08,0:28:13.17,中文,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 扎克 - 最近怎样 伊弗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Hey, Zack. - How's it going, Eph?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.06,0:28:14.46,中文,,0,0,0,,还行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.15,0:28:18.88,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你们在重建这间房\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you're rebuilding this place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.88,0:28:21.85,中文,,0,0,0,,没错 这里放一台\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. Giant screen TV
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.85,0:28:24.42,中文,,0,0,0,,巨型银幕电视 放在这个房间里刚刚好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}over here. Perfect size for a room like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.42,0:28:26.32,中文,,0,0,0,,音响放这里 还有这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Speakers here, and here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.91,0:28:29.10,中文,,0,0,0,,这里会变得焕然一新\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This'll be a great new space for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.10,0:28:32.50,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道这样很尴尬\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Listen... I know this is awkward,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.51,0:28:34.64,中文,,0,0,0,,但我不太希望这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but I don't want it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.55,0:28:36.26,中文,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.44,0:28:39.78,中文,,0,0,0,,让她幸福就好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.78,0:28:42.95,中文,,0,0,0,,让他们都过得幸福 除此之外别无所求\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just make them happy. That's all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.17,0:28:45.73,中文,,0,0,0,,放心吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.06,0:28:49.45,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 哦 好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh. Oh, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.13,0:28:50.64,中文,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.51,0:28:53.86,中文,,0,0,0,,我能和我儿子说几句话吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mind if I speak with my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.31,0:28:57.20,中文,,0,0,0,,当然可以 我打赌 过段时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, of course. You know, in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.20,0:29:00.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会成为很好的朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I bet you and I will become good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.80,0:29:02.55,中文,,0,0,0,,有可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.93,0:29:05.15,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 扎克 扎克 我马上要走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, Zack, Zack, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.93,0:29:08.71,中文,,0,0,0,,因为那架飞机的事 我知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because of that plane. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.28,0:29:10.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我想跟你谈谈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wanted to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.44,0:29:13.00,中文,,0,0,0,,- 明天的监护权听证会 - 行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- the custody hearing tomorrow. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.20,0:29:15.86,中文,,0,0,0,,- 别迟到就行了 - 不会的 一定不会的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Just don't be late. - I won't. I won't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.02,0:29:17.95,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我发誓 - 你想谈什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I mean it. - So what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.06,0:29:19.71,中文,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.11,0:29:24.51,中文,,0,0,0,,对我们来说 会是个尴尬的场合 对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It is a weird situation, huh, for all of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.57,0:29:27.08,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈说法官会问各种问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mom says the judge will ask all kinds of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.28,0:29:30.03,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 他会的 也可能是个女的问 不管是谁反正都会问的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, he will. Or she will. Whoever it is, they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.71,0:29:33.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你想好怎么说了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Have you thought about what you were gonna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.33,0:29:35.02,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈说我怎么想就怎么说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mom says I should just say how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.22,0:29:37.83,中文,,0,0,0,,那是当然 就按照你内心的想法说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Absolutely. Just be honest. Just from your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.24,0:29:39.93,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你打算怎么说 - 我 和你一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What are you gonna say? - Me? Same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.42,0:29:43.37,中文,,0,0,0,,就说些我的想法 我会说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My feelings. I'm gonna say
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.37,0:29:45.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你是这个世界上对我来说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you're the most important person
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.80,0:29:46.87,中文,,0,0,0,,最重要的人 因为这就是事实\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in the world to me, because you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.88,0:29:49.84,中文,,0,0,0,,- 还会说我想要共同抚养权 - 那是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- and that I want joint custody. - What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.42,0:29:52.38,中文,,0,0,0,,意思是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.73,0:29:55.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你和我相处的时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that you get to spend as much time with me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.91,0:29:56.45,中文,,0,0,0,,跟你和妈妈相处的时间一样多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}as you do with your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.45,0:29:58.35,中文,,0,0,0,,你也是这么想的 对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I know that's what you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.35,0:30:00.35,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 但是如果你老是这么忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah... But if you're always so busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.36,0:30:02.39,中文,,0,0,0,,不会的 等这次事件解决之后一定不会了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I won't be, not after I put this case to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.08,0:30:05.86,中文,,0,0,0,,你老是这么说 我知道你是认真的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You always say that. And I know you mean it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.86,0:30:09.26,中文,,0,0,0,,- 但从来没实现过 - 扎克 扎克 看着我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- but it's never true. - Zack, Zack, look at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.28,0:30:12.04,中文,,0,0,0,,这一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This time,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.31,0:30:12.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我一定说到做到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.33,0:30:22.29,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(894,520)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}皇后{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}区{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)} 阿斯{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}托{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)}里亚{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)} 31{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}街
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.97,0:30:34.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我以为你不会来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I didn't think you were gonna show.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.20,0:30:37.26,中文,,0,0,0,,履行承诺是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keeping commitments is...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.84,0:30:39.97,中文,,0,0,0,,治疗过程的一部分\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is part of my recovery process.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.02,0:31:09.85,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 我叫伊弗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hi, my name's Eph.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.55,0:31:11.26,中文,,0,0,0,,我是酗酒者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm an alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.77,0:31:16.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我已经一年零十一天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've been sober one year
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.39,0:31:18.93,中文,,0,0,0,,没有沾酒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and eleven days.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.68,0:31:21.17,中文,,0,0,0,,正在接受治疗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm in therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.48,0:31:23.53,中文,,0,0,0,,试着认清自己\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Learning about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.42,0:31:26.84,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一趟漫长的旅行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's a journey of discovery. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.73,0:31:31.77,中文,,0,0,0,,医生说我兼具被动和主动攻击性性格\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm passive-aggressive and actively aggressive,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.80,0:31:33.88,中文,,0,0,0,,这很少见 他们是这么跟我说的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}which is a rare combination, I'm told.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.22,0:31:39.02,中文,,0,0,0,,让我想想 还有什么 我是控制狂 以自我为中心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's see, what else? I'm controlling. I'm self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.08,0:31:41.11,中文,,0,0,0,,和家人感情疏远\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm emotionally distant for my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.66,0:31:42.95,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 还有最坏的一点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, and the greatest sin of all:
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.95,0:31:43.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱工作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I love my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.84,0:31:48.35,中文,,0,0,0,,但这些我都认了 因为都是我应得的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I'm taking it all in, you know, I'm owning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.71,0:31:53.37,中文,,0,0,0,,这对我产生了很大的影响\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And it's really making a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.73,0:31:56.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我的妻子要和我离婚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My wife's divorcing me,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.85,0:31:59.89,中文,,0,0,0,,和另外一个家伙搞上了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and screwing this new dude...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.89,0:32:02.15,中文,,0,0,0,,就在我的房子 我的房间里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in my bed. In my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.16,0:32:04.56,中文,,0,0,0,,房子的房贷甚至还是我在还着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}on which I'm still making payments.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.71,0:32:10.33,中文,,0,0,0,,老毛病又犯了 是吧 理查德 我的担保人说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There I go again, right, Richard? My sponsor says
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.35,0:32:12.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我总是用讽刺的方式来逃避真实情感\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that I use sarcasm to avoid my real feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.64,0:32:15.91,中文,,0,0,0,,因为如果我是真心爱凯利 我会替她感到高兴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that if I truly loved Kelly, I would be happy for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.40,0:32:18.07,中文,,0,0,0,,而不是憎恨她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wouldn't resent her...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.02,0:32:22.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我已经努力了 理查德\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm trying, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.86,0:32:25.91,中文,,0,0,0,,但我走得很艰难\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But it is a very steep hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.12,0:32:30.85,中文,,0,0,0,,就在我来之前我才见过他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I saw them right before I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.85,0:32:32.55,中文,,0,0,0,,他们三个在一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All three of them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.62,0:32:37.99,中文,,0,0,0,,做着我一直都没有时间去做的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Doing things I never had time to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.99,0:32:39.37,中文,,0,0,0,,到现在我都没时间去做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}still don't have time to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.09,0:32:42.35,中文,,0,0,0,,我想喝一杯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wanted a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.77,0:32:46.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我走之后经过了一家酒吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I passed a bar after I left there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.93,0:32:47.48,中文,,0,0,0,,但我还是来到了这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.21,0:32:54.60,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我不能失去扎克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because I can't blow it with Zack.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.33,0:32:59.97,中文,,0,0,0,,因为他是我剩下的唯一了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Cuz that I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.97,0:33:07.73,中文,,0,0,0,,他就是我的全部\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's my whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.06,0:33:46.60,中文,,0,0,0,,准备好狂欢了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you ready to party with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.30,0:33:48.22,中文,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.61,0:34:02.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你闻起来真香 尝起来肯定更好美味\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You smell beautiful. I bet you taste even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.05,0:34:11.32,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧 加布 - 没事 没事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You okay, Gabe? - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.32,0:34:12.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我还没从德国时差缓过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm still on German time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.62,0:34:16.43,中文,,0,0,0,,继续不要停 我马上就进入状态\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep the beat going. I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.97,0:34:35.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你咬我 你这混蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You bit me, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.75,0:34:39.78,中文,,0,0,0,,- 狗屎 - 我流血了 他真咬了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Bullshit. - I'm bleeding. He bit me hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.00,0:34:40.57,中文,,0,0,0,,滚出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.82,0:34:44.29,中文,,0,0,0,,快滚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get out! Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.96,0:34:49.46,中文,,0,0,0,,滚 你疯了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Out! You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.62,0:35:13.25,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(878,522)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}皇后{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}区{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)} 圣{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}塞巴{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)}斯{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}蒂安{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}医院
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.17,0:35:11.66,中文,,0,0,0,,情况怎样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.86,0:35:14.42,中文,,0,0,0,,雷德芬刚刚失去了控制\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Redfern just went into a tailspin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.46,0:35:16.28,中文,,0,0,0,,莱斯特和他在一起 这是病情报告\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Lester's with him. Here's the path report.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.29,0:35:17.44,中文,,0,0,0,,从没见过这种情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.31,0:35:23.76,中文,,0,0,0,,太不可思议了 畸变器官 外来细胞\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is crazy: Aberrant, foreign cells...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.76,0:35:25.35,中文,,0,0,0,,多型核现象\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}nuclear pleomorphism.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.33,0:35:28.60,中文,,0,0,0,,双表型外观 就像有什么东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Biphenotypic appearance... It's like something
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.60,0:35:30.63,中文,,0,0,0,,强行占领了他的细胞组织\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}shanghaied his cellular machinery
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.63,0:35:32.53,中文,,0,0,0,,并正在制造着完全不一样的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and is creating something totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.54,0:35:35.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我们已经抑制了他的疼痛和初期流感 不过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've sedated him for the pain, started fluids, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.77,0:35:37.87,中文,,0,0,0,,- 抗体报告送过来没有 - 没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Antibody studies back in yet? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.87,0:35:41.11,中文,,0,0,0,,- 感觉怎么样 多伊尔 - 全身沸腾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- How you feeling, Doyle? - Boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.11,0:35:44.71,中文,,0,0,0,,皮肤有什么在爬行 感觉像吞了一把剃刀 用紫外光\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Skin's crawling. I feel like I swallowed a razor. UV light.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.93,0:35:49.22,中文,,0,0,0,,小心眼睛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Watch your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.45,0:35:53.72,中文,,0,0,0,,伤疤 和航班其他受害者一样的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A scar. Same place as the airline victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.72,0:35:55.09,中文,,0,0,0,,只是它恢复太快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It just healed so fast
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.09,0:35:56.63,中文,,0,0,0,,没有紫外光照射根本看不见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we couldn't see it without UV light.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.63,0:35:57.73,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗 看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eph, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.22,0:36:07.47,中文,,0,0,0,,金 找到巴恩斯 告诉他雷德芬情况变严峻了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim, find Barnes. Tell him that Redfern's gone critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.47,0:36:09.17,中文,,0,0,0,,他发现你在治疗雷德芬的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's gonna be really pissed when he finds out
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.17,0:36:11.11,中文,,0,0,0,,肯定会非常生气 没空管这个 告诉他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you've been treating him. I don't give a shit! Tell him
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.11,0:36:12.37,中文,,0,0,0,,有一个幸存者现在非常虚弱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that one of the survivors is very sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.42,0:36:14.04,中文,,0,0,0,,还有我们需要召回剩下的幸存者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tell him we need to corral the rest of the survivors
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.14,0:36:15.48,中文,,0,0,0,,以及一切和他们接触过的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and anybody they've had contact with.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.57,0:36:16.69,中文,,0,0,0,,现在就去 好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.93,0:36:19.07,中文,,0,0,0,,解剖室现在应该有些成果了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The autopsies should have turned something up by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.18,0:36:20.42,中文,,0,0,0,,班尼特医生还是不接电话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Bennett is still not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.46,0:36:21.73,中文,,0,0,0,,又直接转入语音箱了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It went straight to voice mail again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.04,0:36:24.48,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 如果到现在还无动于衷的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, if the mountain won't come to Mahomet...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.02,0:36:26.15,中文,,0,0,0,,那我们直接去停尸房\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're going to the morgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.08,0:36:30.23,中文,,0,0,0,,古德温泽博士 我是疾控中心站的劳里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Goodweather? This is Laurie from the CDC exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.23,0:36:32.89,中文,,0,0,0,,- 有一个叫加里阿诺特的打了过来 - 好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- There's a Gary Arnot calling. - Yeah, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.90,0:36:35.06,中文,,0,0,0,,你好 是医生吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hello? Yes, Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.06,0:36:36.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我是加里阿诺特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}this is Gary Arnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.70,0:36:39.03,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我是艾玛的 - 我知道你是谁 阿诺特先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I'm Emma's... - I know who you are, Mr. Arnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.04,0:36:41.40,中文,,0,0,0,,首先 我想为我之前做的事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}First of all, I just wanted to say
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.40,0:36:43.71,中文,,0,0,0,,向你道歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that I'm sorry for what I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.26,0:36:44.89,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(820,520)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}皇后{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}区{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}牙买加{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}住宅{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)}区{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)} 都铎{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}路
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.71,0:36:46.44,中文,,0,0,0,,还有 谢谢你把我的宝贝女儿送回了家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and to thank you for sending my little girl home to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.97,0:36:50.28,中文,,0,0,0,,什么 你是说有人把她的尸体送回去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What? Are you saying someone released her body to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.75,0:36:51.84,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不是尸体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, not her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.78,0:36:55.22,中文,,0,0,0,,艾玛还活着 今天早上她出现在家门口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Emma's alive. She showed up on my doorstep this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.80,0:36:58.32,中文,,0,0,0,,呃 阿诺特先生 我有点糊涂了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh, Mr. Arnot, I'm a little confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.32,0:36:59.46,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你的意思是 - 你不相信我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Are you telling me... - You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.73,0:37:02.12,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 无所谓\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know what? Fine, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.12,0:37:04.59,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我只是 - 我女儿在家很安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I'm just trying to... - My daughter's home safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.59,0:37:06.70,中文,,0,0,0,,反正这才是最重要的 非常感谢你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's all that matters. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.33,0:37:10.15,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得她可能还活着吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you think it's possible she's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.53,0:37:12.37,中文,,0,0,0,,他受了打击 看见的是幻觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's in shock. He's seeing ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.37,0:37:13.86,中文,,0,0,0,,当时我在座位上检查了她 她已经死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I examined her in her seat, she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.15,0:37:16.53,中文,,0,0,0,,我们登上那架飞机的时候 每个人看起来都死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When we boarded that plane, everybody looked dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.64,0:37:17.91,中文,,0,0,0,,然后四个人醒了过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Then four of them woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.71,0:37:21.98,中文,,0,0,0,,这些虫子会不会使人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Could these worms somehow induce
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.98,0:37:23.33,中文,,0,0,0,,进入类似冬眠的状态\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}some sort of state of hibernation?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.28,0:37:25.77,中文,,0,0,0,,就像舌蝇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Like tsetse flies?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.52,0:37:28.02,中文,,0,0,0,,马上我们就会知道了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We'll find out in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.00,0:37:30.46,中文,,0,0,0,,如果她死了 她会在停尸房里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If she's dead, she'll be at the morgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.53,0:37:39.97,中文,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.86,0:37:43.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道您不喜欢听\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know you don't wanna hear this,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.50,0:37:45.40,中文,,0,0,0,,但我跟随您很久了 听过很多医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but I've been with you a long time and listened
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.40,0:37:47.60,中文,,0,0,0,,对你许下各种各样的承诺\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to a lot of doctors promise you a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.46,0:37:50.08,中文,,0,0,0,,他们什么能做什么不能做 我都看在眼里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've seen what can be done and what can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.34,0:37:54.78,中文,,0,0,0,,这些人 他们在欺骗你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}These people... They're deceiving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.37,0:37:57.88,中文,,0,0,0,,这些人有一种\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}These people have power
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.88,0:37:59.44,中文,,0,0,0,,你完全意想不到的能力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}beyond anything you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.75,0:38:04.85,中文,,0,0,0,,到时候 你也会从中受益的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In time, you also will benefit from that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.48,0:38:07.77,中文,,0,0,0,,留在车里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stay with the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.44,0:38:09.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我必须一个人面对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need to do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.57,0:38:56.68,中文,,0,0,0,,太阳已经落下了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The sun has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.41,0:39:02.78,中文,,0,0,0,,你很幸运 帕尔默先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You are very fortunate, Mr. Palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.86,0:39:07.46,中文,,0,0,0,,他选中你来见证这光荣的时刻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He has chosen you to bear witness to his glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.64,0:39:26.00,中文,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到新世界\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Welcome to the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.10,0:39:31.42,中文,,0,0,0,,你大老远把我带过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You brought me all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.68,0:39:38.51,中文,,0,0,0,,都不打算看我一眼吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aren't you going to look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.91,0:40:07.31,中文,,0,0,0,,你好 有人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hello? Anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.09,0:40:12.93,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fs50\pos(1006,506)}{\alpha&FF&\t(0,400,\alpha&0&)\pos(734,512)}首席{\alpha&FF&\t(400,800,\alpha&0&)}法医{\alpha&FF&\t(800,1200,\alpha&0&)}办公室{\alpha&FF&\t(1200,1600,\alpha&0&)}\N\h曼哈顿{\alpha&FF&\t(1600,2000,\alpha&0&)} 东{\alpha&FF&\t(2000,2400,\alpha&0&)}30{\alpha&FF&\t(2400,2800,\alpha&0&)}街
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.13,0:40:16.02,中文,,0,0,0,,班尼特医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Bennett?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.57,0:40:20.17,中文,,0,0,0,,班尼特医生 你还好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Bennett, you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.94,0:40:28.82,中文,,0,0,0,,禁区\N严禁入内
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.02,0:40:39.55,中文,,0,0,0,,有人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.33,0:40:57.40,中文,,0,0,0,,袋子是空的 每个都是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Every bag is empty. Every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.87,0:41:21.54,中文,,0,0,0,,是你把灯关了的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.71,0:41:27.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我抱你出来吧 水都凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.42,0:41:33.47,中文,,0,0,0,,要聊天的话 我可以跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.14,0:41:38.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我会慢慢听你说
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.64,0:41:44.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我待会儿放狮子王的曲子 我们一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.94,0:41:46.10,中文,,0,0,0,,你饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.10,0:41:47.77,中文,,0,0,0,,饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.28,0:41:59.95,中文,,0,0,0,,来 先擦干
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.91,0:42:05.71,中文,,0,0,0,,来
